      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior has noticeable body damage and paint deterioration, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear. Mechanically, it needs several repairs to be fully roadworthy, making it best suited as a project car or for parts. Please come prepared for a vehicle that reflects its age and lack of recent maintenance.",
