    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major electronic features are fully functional. While you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, such as small stone chips on the hood or light interior scuffing, the car remains clean and dependable. It is a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
