    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project seekers and DIY experts! This vehicle is looking for a dedicated new owner to bring it back to its former glory. While it requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it serves as a fantastic foundation for a full restoration or a valuable source of parts for your next build. Grab this opportunity to own a vehicle with great bones and endless potential at an affordable price!",
